timing_report...ary_mean_sigma(25.10)    timing_report...ary_mean_sigma(25.10)

Name
       timing_report_socv_summary_mean_sigma

Syntax
       timing_report_socv_summary_mean_sigma {true | false}

       Default: false

       Prints  the  report header in new format when the report_timing command
       is run in SOCV mode. The new header contains nsigma,  mean,  and  sigma
       details.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

